com.khaledbakhit.api.rslib.dataset

Class DataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khaledbakhit.api.rslib.dataset.DataSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DataSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    DataSet Object represents a DataSet file containing cases. Dealing with DataSet input as Files has low memory consumption but requires more processing time every time you read from disk. However, dealing with DataSet input as DataSet Object (store in memory) sharply decreases processing time (read from main memory rather than disk) but creates a much bigger foot print in memory.
    Since:
    4.0
    Version:
    20/08/2013
    Author:
